title: These are the names of the Umpqua Community College shooting victims
text:
Nine people died Thursday after a gunman opened fire at Umpqua Community College students and teachers. Douglas County Sheriff John Hanlin released their names during a news conference on Friday. Here are their names:
Lucero Alcaraz, of Roseburg, 19 Quinn Glen Cooper, of Roseburg, 18 Lucas Eibel of Roseburg, 18 Jason Johnson, Winston, 33 Lawrence Levine, of Glide, 67 Sarena Dawn Moore, Myrtle Creek, 44 Treven Anspach, of Sutherlin, 20 Rebecka Carnes, Myrtle Creek, 18 Kim Saltmarsh Dietz, of Roseburg, 59 â€” The Oregonian/OregonLive
